{"tid":1038923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【預算案】撥款 1.5 億元　開發一帶一路「爭議解決網上平台」","createTime":"2019-02-27T05:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T11:33:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"024b40ab83b02ec6f7f7cd7962e75dde7c88385c","tid":1038923,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/bay-04_lnwKI_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fbay-04_lnwKI_1200x0.png&h=9b453793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波今天發表 2019/20 年度財政預算案，提出撥款 1.5 億元，支持非政府機構開發「爭議解決網上平台」，為「一帶一路」沿線經濟體解決爭議。<br />\n<br />\n去年的《施政報告》提出，要推動香港作為「一帶一路」的國際爭議解決服務中心，包括支持非政府機構籌建網上「一帶一路」仲裁及調解平台，「促使香港提供便捷和具成本效益的網上爭議解決服務」。<br />\n<br />\n今年的預算案，就進一步提出將會撥款 1.5 億元，支持該網上平台的開發及初期運作。平台會利便包括本港以至「一帶一路」沿線經濟體的中小微企，促成交易並避免及解決爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/預算案-撥款-1-5-億元-開發一帶一路-爭議解決網上平台/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88-%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE-1-5-%E5%84%84%E5%85%83-%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF-%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%2F&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6UB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=e24280bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88-%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE-1-5-%E5%84%84%E5%85%83-%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF-%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%2F&h=5d70ab7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/預算案-撥款-1-5-億元-開發一帶一路-爭議解決網上平台/</a>"},{"pid":"69bf3661a9e7f4573272249f1529ecc25ca4eb85","tid":1038923,"uid":178875,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"維穩費黎講太少wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br